## ⚙️ Variables de Entorno

Definidas en `application.yml` e inyectables como variables de entorno en Docker:

```yaml
server:
  port: 8080

spring:
  application:
    name: api-gateway

  cloud:
    gateway:
      routes:
        # ── auth-service ──────────────────────────────────────────────
        - id: auth-register
          uri: http://auth-service:8081
          predicates:
            - Path=/api/auth/register
          filters:
            - StripPrefix=0

        - id: auth-login
          uri: http://auth-service:8081
          predicates:
            - Path=/api/auth/login
          filters:
            - StripPrefix=0

        - id: auth-service
          uri: http://auth-service:8081
          predicates:
            - Path=/api/auth/**
          filters:
            - StripPrefix=0

        # ── account-service ───────────────────────────────────────────
        - id: account-service
          uri: http://account-service:8082
          predicates:
            - Path=/api/accounts/**
          filters:
            - StripPrefix=0

        # ── payment-orchestrator ──────────────────────────────────────
        - id: payment-orchestrator
          uri: http://payment-orchestrator:8083
          predicates:
            - Path=/api/payments/**
          filters:
            - StripPrefix=0

        # ── ledger-service ────────────────────────────────────────────
        - id: ledger-service
          uri: http://ledger-service:8084
          predicates:
            - Path=/api/ledger/**
          filters:
            - StripPrefix=0

  security:
    oauth2:
      resourceserver:
        jwt:
          issuer-uri: ${JWT_ISSUER_URI}
```

| Variable | Descripción | Ejemplo |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `JWT_ISSUER_URI` | URI del `auth-service` para validar firma JWT (JWKS) | `http://auth-service:8081` |

> El gateway no necesita credenciales de base de datos, Kafka ni API keys externas.
Su única dependencia de configuración es el `issuer-uri` para descargar la clave pública de validación de tokens.

